/// @G_URI_FLAGS_ENCODED_FRAGMENT: Same as %G_URI_FLAGS_ENCODED, for the
/// fragment only.
/// @G_URI_FLAGS_SCHEME_NORMALIZE: A scheme-based normalization will be applied.
