/// (deprecated) %G_FILE_MONITOR_SEND_MOVED flag is set
/// @G_FILE_MONITOR_EVENT_RENAMED: the file was renamed within the
/// current directory -- only sent if the %G_FILE_MONITOR_WATCH_MOVES
